Annotation Type Experimental


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE,FIELD,METHOD,PARAMETER,CONSTRUCTOR,LOCAL_VARIABLE,PACKAGE})
public @interface Experimental
    An experimental user-facing API. Experimental APIs are quickly evolving and might change or be removed in minor versions. Inspired by org.apache.spark.annotation.Experimental
